Quickstrike:




Quickstrike kept his head ducked to the water. He lightly snapped his large 
claw, not taking his eyes off his prey. "Yeah," he replied to Stingtra. 
"Come on over here! Ah'll catch ya one!" He plunged his foreclaw into the 
water, and brought it back out with a long fish between the pinchers. He 
flung it towards Stingtra. His mind was off his stomach. Hunting fish was 
becoming a pastime.
